docs Requests
    Accepts HTTP connections on a port and emits parsed requests.
    Each emitted value is an HttpRequest with conn_id, method, path, query, headers, and body fields.
done

source Requests
    take port as long
    emit req as HttpRequest
    fail error as text
body
    srv = http.server.listen(port)
    on :request from http.server.accept(srv) to req
        emit req
    done
done

test Requests
    # Source: I/O dependent — stub test
    ok = true
    must ok == true
done
